{
  "texts": [
    "This process results in the formulation of reasoning queries (e.g., is Harry Potter capable of instructing broomstick flying).",
    "• HellaSwag (Zellers et al, 2019a).",
    "The HellaSwag dataset is curated for evaluating common-sense natural language reasoning.",
    "Each query includes a scenario and four conceivable outcomes, tasking models with deducing the most reasonable conclusion.",
    "Human-validated incorrect responses aim to mislead the model."
  ]
}